sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Producer
    participant K as Kafka
    participant S as Spark Streaming
    participant M as MongoDB

    P->>K: Publish price tick (crypto_raw)
    K->>S: Read micro-batch
    S->>S: Parse & watermark (10 min)
    S->>S: Window aggregation (20 min / 5 min slide)
    S->>M: Write window_stats
    S->>S: Compute indicators (SMA, RSI, VWAP, Bollinger)
    S->>M: Write realtime_prices
    S-->>M: Write alert (if |change_24h| > 5%)
